{
  "stem": "8370.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, this is a woman who had a hobby to collect tattoo skin, human skin, to make lampshade, to make albums cover, books cover, and so on.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the story started like that, that I was a witness in her court case.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because when they prepared the courtroom for her process, I walked in by coincidence.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I saw a beautiful lampshade with a bunch of roses on from human skin.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I recognized this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a young German who had-- was with me in Auschwitz and had on his left arm this beautiful bunch of roses tattooed-- leaf greens, green leaves and red flower-- three or four, I don't remember now.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I recognized this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on this was a ticket, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Written on the ticket was the, was a, how you call it-- a unknown.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On some of them wasn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For example, she had a arm, a piece of skin from the arm with a number of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was easy to find out who it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in this case, I say-- I ran to the prosecutor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I say, listen, old chap!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know this chap!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know it was a German prisoner, political prisoner, a German one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember that he was in-- he told me, when they ask him why he's in the army in the concentration camp, he told me that he was in a scouting movement before.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as you maybe know, they-- Hitler arrested all the top people from the scouting when he came to power.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because scouting was a-- I would say, competition to his Hitlerjugend movement.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he had to destroy the scouting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyhow, so it was, you know-- and I, I have done this for couple of-- well, more than one year, interrogating the people.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
